metadata.title: Regional Education Attendance Areas

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources, Division of Support Services-Land Records Information Section

metadata.description: Data Type: Boundaries  ; The Regional Education Attendance Area (REAA) boundaries are important to state funding of School programs throughout Alaska. The boundaries were derived from source documents provided by the Alaska Department of Community and Regional Affairs, and boundaries extracted from state LAS Land file.
